name: Argon SDK & Documentation
body:
### Get the ArgonSDK Sample Code for Argon2 Isotope
You can checkout all the ArgonSDK Sample Code by cloning the ArgonSDK repository.
```
$ git clone https://github.com/argonsdk/Argon-SDK.git
```

### Documentation
[Go to the Documentation Browser](http://argonsdk.github.com/apidocs)
